    note right of maybeListener
        addDropTargetListener() is allowed here (listener may or may not be set from constructor).
        Calling addDropTargetListener() when a listener is already present throws TooManyListenersException.
        Drag event methods have no effect if DropTarget is not active (controlled via setActive()).
    end note

    note right of HasListener
        addDropTargetListener() throws TooManyListenersException in this state (unicast source).
        removeDropTargetListener() returns to maybeListener state.
    end note
